data.description: Welcome to this well-maintained home with nice curb appeal!! This 3 bed, 3 bath, 2 car garage home has a large tiled foyer.  LVP floors in the living room, dining area, and bedrooms add to the appeal of this home.  The Living room features a decorative brick fireplace and the seller only used an electric log insert for ambience. The updated kitchen provides convenient work space and handsome granite countertops that complement the cabinets, tiled floors, and newer stainless steel appliances.  The large dining area allows for a great place for family dinners/gatherings and an extension to this is the Trex deck that is covered great for outside gatherings, also the deck has an uncovered section with a sun shade sail that will be included. A large master bedroom with a door leading to the deck and a master 3/4 bathroom with a walk-in shower. The two other bedrooms are a nice size and a full bathroom in the hallway.  The laundry room is on the main level and there is a half bathroom off the laundry room. The small finished basement is a bonus area it can be used as a conforming additional bedroom or it has many other possibilities such as an office, man cave, TV room, etc. The entry to the crawlspace is in the basement and can provide extra storage - there is a light switch for this area. The backyard is completely fenced, has a shed, and a side yard that provides additional parking for a trailer/boat.  A high-efficiency Aerocool Evaporative cooler was purchased in 2022.
